        <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">616 818 5413</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Alignment="Center" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.00" OutlineLevel="1" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
        <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="Underline">Logline</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.00" OutlineLevel="1" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
        <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">In a last-ditch effort to reinvent herself, a struggling educator must win the host role in the beloved children’s tv series, only to face the original host’s legacy and a public resistant to inclusivity.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Alignment="Center" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.00" OutlineLevel="1" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
      <Paragraph Alignment="Center" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.00" OutlineLevel="1" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
      <Paragraph Alignment="Center" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.00" OutlineLevel="1" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
        <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="Underline">Episode</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.00" OutlineLevel="1" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
        <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">The network officially pushes Ray in front of the camera as Aurora’s crazy sidekick. She struggles with the educational pause and is resentful of being second best again, but after seeing how her blunt communication style resonates with children like her brother Kwan, she accepts the role. The network screens the 10-minute pilot episode, Milky Way Sick Day to a test audience.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Alignment="Center" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.00" OutlineLevel="1" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
      <Paragraph Alignment="Center" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.00" OutlineLevel="1" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
      <Paragraph Alignment="Center" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.00" OutlineLevel="1" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
        <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="Underline">Plot Summary</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.00" OutlineLevel="1" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
        <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">The network officially pushes Ray in front of the camera as Aurora’s crazy sidekick. She struggles with the educational pause and is resentful of being second best again, but after seeing how her blunt communication style resonates with children like her brother Kwan, she accepts the role. The network screens the 10-minute pilot episode, Milky Way Sick Day to a test audience.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Alignment="Center" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.00" OutlineLevel="1" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
